the paper has been the leading communicator of the party line 
since its first edition was issued june 15 1948 
its stolid gray pages have signaled to chinese and the outside 
world key developments such as the rise of the cult of mao 
tsetung the start of the far leftist cultural revolution in 1966 
and its end in 1976 with the arrest of maos wife jiang qing and 
her fellow radicals 
