after he had received three calls with specific kidnapping threats 
he said he had no idea who made the calls 
we felt it just precautionary to move her and she is 
comfortable though she doesnt like being away and we dont like 
it either shell remain out of state until all this has simmered 
down brittain said 
brittains other child thomas 21 has remained at home 
