called mieras fast manipulative 
this whole story breaks down to a guy whos so outrageous and 
just happens to be mexican johnson said nobody comes to help 
me because im white 
in march 1987 a jury found that miera committed battery under 
civil law by forcibly kissing johnson in december 1984 the jury 
awarded johnson 375000 in damages but district judge john 
weyrens of litchfield reduced the amount to 125000 the jurys 
decision and the judges award reduction were upheld by the 
minnesota court of appeals on june 7 
